{"tid":1803399,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[再無hollandbankcheque]荷蘭元旦日起  棄用Holland統一國名為Netherlands","createTime":"2019-12-30T07:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T07:44:34.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"665ed54a8f8b088b956ecf8c7b06e13eabacb413","tid":1803399,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"荷蘭政府宣布明年1月1日起將停用「Holland」的稱號, 統一改用正式國名「Netherlands」，屆時所有公司、大使館、政府部門及大學都只可使用「Netherlands」這個官方叫法。<br />\n<br />\n今次更改將花費20萬歐元，是荷蘭重塑國家形象計劃的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭旅遊部門一直以「Holland」作旅遊推廣，但「Holland」並不是荷蘭整個國家的正式名稱，而是指12個省中的其中兩個。於元旦日起荷蘭的國家標誌亦將由「Holland」改為「Netherlands」的縮寫「NL」，並以荷蘭國花橙色鬱金香相結合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.984218/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.984218%2F2&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3Kkaof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=0cb09704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.984218/2</a>"},{"pid":"51259c576365cad52606d3c0b4f07b6a44af5020","tid":1803399,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"Netherland叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a524c57eb260f2794ea0ed6b33ff8c3f83ab9b4f","tid":1803399,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3Kkaof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=2474c931\" target=\"_blank\">http